sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy-Compatible Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant BBR as Body-Based Router (BBR)<br/>9004/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker (EPP)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelServer as Model Server Pod<br/>(vLLM/SGLang/Triton)
    participant MetricsEP as Model Server /metrics<br/>HTTP

    Note over EPP,K8sAPI: Startup: Watch CRDs & Pods
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, InferenceObjective,<br/>InferenceModelRewrite, Pods
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: CRD & Pod events (streaming)
    BBR->>K8sAPI: Watch ConfigMaps (bbr-managed=true)
    K8sAPI-->>BBR: ConfigMap events (streaming)

    Note over EPP,MetricsEP: Continuous: Metrics Scraping (every 50ms default)
    loop Every refresh-metrics-interval
        EPP->>MetricsEP: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP (InsecureSkipVerify)
        MetricsEP-->>EPP: KV cache util, queue depth,<br/>running requests, LoRA info
    end

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 1: Inference Request with Body-Based Routing
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>BBR: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 TLS (self-signed)
    Note right of BBR: Parse JSON body,<br/>extract model name,<br/>resolve LoRA→base model
    BBR-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>(inject model-name header)

    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 TLS (self-signed)
    Note right of EPP: Flow control admission<br/>→ Filter endpoints<br/>→ Score endpoints<br/>→ Pick best endpoint
    EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>(set target-endpoint header)

    Gateway->>ModelServer: Forward inference request<br/>to selected endpoint
    ModelServer-->>Gateway: Inference response<br/>(streaming or unary)
    Gateway-->>Client: Response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 2: Direct Routing (no BBR)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS, model in header
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 TLS
    EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>(target-endpoint header)
    Gateway->>ModelServer: Forward to selected endpoint
    ModelServer-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: Response

    Note over EPP,MetricsEP: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    EPP->>MetricsEP: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (configurable)
    MetricsEP-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics
    Note right of EPP: Update datastore:<br/>KV cache utilization,<br/>queue depth,<br/>running requests,<br/>LoRA adapter status
